<br>
I like this idea a lot. Straight cumulative wouldn't work well for the reasons stated, but having both would be great. Of course it would need to be tuned to still make agro managment non-trivial, but I think it could be done. I would like to see:<br>
<br>
1. AE taunt - works 100% of the time with the Z-axis problem on tall mobs fixed<br>
2. Taunt 1 - cycles every 3-5 seconds and adds cumulative taunt equalt to taunt skill/5<br>
3. Taunt 2 - cycles every 10 seconds with a 20% chance to move to the top of the hate list +1 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=frodlin7th>Frodlin7th</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/cons RED</span><br>  Posts: 306<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/8/03 3:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2878.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cummulative taunt?</span><hr size=1> I think they should leave the friggin taunt button the way it is and go for somewhere that doesn't involve breaking the way the game has worked since day 1.<br>
<br>
Such as.... (imagine hearing this from me) Fletched Arrows that are warrior only which add hate on a successful hit.  I'd call them Arrows of Frodlinic Rage <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=2878.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=2878.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2878.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=2878.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=2878.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2878.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2878.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><